nce\": \"Ina 2021 interview, Hocker said he runs \\\"because I have a God-given talent.\\\"\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just feel God has given me the gift of running, and my job is to give it my best,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow American runner Yared Nuguse, meanwhile, took the bronze medal in the race, marking the first time since 1912 that two American athletes have been on the men's 1,500-meter podium.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2401, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fellow\", \"score\": 0.9699595935543966, \"rank\": 0.03092730454452143, \"text\": \"Fellow\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fellow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fellow\"}, {\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7971938519879657, \"rank\": 0.2543999842685583, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}, {\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7971938519879657, \"rank\": 0.2543999842685583, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'EWTN News In Depth' video highlights from the Aug. 16 episode.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hocker is the first U.S. athlete t